name: Realty Compass
overview:
Realtycompass.com is a professional e -commerce real estate portal offering comprehensive listing of residential projects across 12 cities. The website www.realtycompass.com will offer exhaustive, unbiased information about projects available in the city.

Realtycompass.com also believes in giving wider choices to customers hence do not charge any fee to builders to showcase the project. www.realtycompass.com will also provide a holistic home buying experience with value added services like – legal consulting and interior solutions. The website will be officially launched on 15th November’2012.

RealtyCompass.com is all about choices, convenience, and relevance. With over 6000 residential properties for sale in Bangalore, Chennai, Hyderabad and Coimbatore alone, RealtyCompass aims to be the one stop solution for all property needs in India.
